{
  "id": "62f701351ff461001d48f5f3",
  "title": "帰省",
  "created": 1660354872,
  "updated": 1733023291,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62f701351ff461001d48f5f3",
      "text": "帰省",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354872,
      "updated": 1660354872
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70137e6003500009b4042",
      "text": "帰省(きせい)という言葉は（[hatori.icon]が調べた限りでは）[唐代]の[詩人][朱慶餘]の[漢詩]「[送張景宣下第東歸]」に由来する",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1660354872,
      "updated": 1733014091
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4043",
      "text": "[送張景宣下第東歸]（歸揚州覲省）",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1666266474
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4044",
      "text": ">歸省值花時，閑吟落第詩。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4045",
      "text": ">高情憐道在，公論覺才遺。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4046",
      "text": ">春雨連淮暗，私船過馬遲。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4047",
      "text": ">離心可惆悵，爲有入城期。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4048",
      "text": "[https://zh.m.wikisource.org/zh/%E9%80%81%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%AF%E5%AE%A3%E4%B8%8B%E7%AC%AC%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%B8 送張景宣下第東歸 - 维基文库，自由的图书馆]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4049",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404a",
      "text": "冒頭の「歸」は「帰」の[旧字体]であり、したがって歸省＝帰省である",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404b",
      "text": "この詩は[全唐詩]巻514に載っているようだ（[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%A8%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9 全唐詩 - Wikipedia]）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404c",
      "text": "　[https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=en&chapter=369701 御定全唐詩 : 卷五百十四 - Chinese Text Project]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404d",
      "text": "　[https://www.kanripo.org/text/KR4h0140/514?query=%E9%80%81%E5%BC%B5%E6%99%AF%E5%AE%A3%E4%B8%8B%E7%AC%AC%E6%9D%B1%E6%AD%B8#514-6b Kanripo 漢籍リポジトリ : KR4h0140 御定全唐詩-清-聖祖玄燁]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404e",
      "text": "日本語訳は誰かに任せた！[hatori.icon]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b404f",
      "text": "　機械翻訳ではあまりうまくいかない",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "645619665e90c00000e905bb",
      "text": "　全唐詩にあるなら江戸時代の文献から訓読を探せそう[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683364197,
      "updated": 1683364218
    },
    {
      "id": "645619845e90c00000e905bd",
      "text": "　　国立国会図書館デジタルコレクションあたりを頑張ればなんとか…",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683364227,
      "updated": 1683364251
    },
    {
      "id": "62f709f0b8bbfc000020cf70",
      "text": "学校で[漢文]習ったことあるしちょっとは読めるかなと思ったが一文字たりともわからんもんだ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1660357105,
      "updated": 1660357161
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70a4eb8bbfc000020cf72",
      "text": "\t読み下せたとしても、詩を読み慣れてないと何が言いたいのかわからん感じの雰囲気がある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1660357199,
      "updated": 1660357241
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70197e6003500009b4061",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354968,
      "updated": 1660354968
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70196e6003500009b4060",
      "text": "参考：[https://rnavi.ndl.go.jp/jp/guides/theme_asia_16.html 漢詩の出典｜リサーチ・ナビ｜国立国会図書館]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354966,
      "updated": 1660354966
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4050",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4051",
      "text": ">帰省の由来・語源",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4052",
      "text": ">唐代から見える漢語で、「帰」は「帰郷する」の意。「省」は「父母を顧みる」の意で使われる。つまり、「帰省」とは、本来は家を離れていた者が故郷に戻って、父母を顧みて大切にすること。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4053",
      "text": ">日本では江戸時代まではあまり使われなかったが、明治時代から現在と同じ意味で用いられるようになった。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4054",
      "text": "[http://yain.jp/i/%E5%B8%B0%E7%9C%81 帰省(きせい)とは - 由来・語源辞典]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4056",
      "text": "　省みる(かえりみる)ということで、帰省の「省」は反省・内省の「省」と同じ意味をもつようだ",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354880
    },
    {
      "id": "64560bb8e5172d0000311f53",
      "text": "　父母を顧みるというより自分がのんびりするために帰省してる…[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1683360696,
      "updated": 1683360719
    },
    {
      "id": "64560bd5e5172d0000311f54",
      "text": "　 帰(不省)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1683360725,
      "updated": 1683360741
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4057",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660354873
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70426e6003500009b4063",
      "text": "最近では[新型コロナウイルス]感染拡大防止のために、[オンライン帰省]（実際に帰省する代わりに、[ビデオ通話]・[テレビ電話]により連絡を取ること）を推奨されることもある",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355623,
      "updated": 1660355664
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70426e6003500009b4064",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355623,
      "updated": 1660355623
    },
    {
      "id": "62f70138e6003500009b4059",
      "text": "類語：[帰郷]、[里帰り]、[藪入り]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660354873,
      "updated": 1660355031
    },
    {
      "id": "62f701d7e6003500009b4062",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1660355031,
      "updated": 1660355031
    },
    {
      "id": "6456387f5e90c00000b1aaae",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d3f4ce0148e192ff34f1c8d81c0241be][https://gyazo.com/73ccf09ef95863436894fec137f205cc]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683372160,
      "updated": 1683372163
    },
    {
      "id": "645638725e90c00000b1aaad",
      "text": " [礼記]や[令義解]にも「省」が引かれているらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683372146,
      "updated": 1683373072
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1a5e90c000000c81b9",
      "text": " ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373083,
      "updated": 1683373083
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1a5e90c000000c81ba",
      "text": " 大町桂月 (芳衛) , 佐伯常麿 著『誤用便覧 : 机上宝引』,文栄閣,明44.5. 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/862888 (参照 2023-05-06)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373083,
      "updated": 1683373083
    },
    {
      "id": "64563c1c5e90c000000c81bb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373085,
      "updated": 1683373085
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bd75e90c000000c81b3",
      "text": "礼記曲礼篇上",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373016,
      "updated": 1683373089
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bd85e90c000000c81b4",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/b82c93d96311431007cb55c2b59b04e4]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373016,
      "updated": 1683373040
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bf55e90c000000c81b6",
      "text": "小林一郎 著『経書大講』第25巻 大學 禮記抄,平凡社,昭13至15. 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション https://dl.ndl.go.jp/pid/1047122 (参照 2023-05-06)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373046,
      "updated": 1683373046
    },
    {
      "id": "64563bf05e90c000000c81b5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1683373040,
      "updated": 1683373040
    },
    {
      "id": "645638675e90c00000b1aaab",
      "text": "--- GPT",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1683372135,
      "updated": 1733023049
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd549aff09e0000047e92",
      "text": "翻訳して[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023076
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e94",
      "text": ">歸省值花時，閑吟落第詩。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e95",
      "text": ">高情憐道在，公論覺才遺。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e96",
      "text": ">春雨連淮暗，私船過馬遲。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e97",
      "text": ">離心可惆悵，爲有入城期。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd553aff09e0000047ebd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023060,
      "updated": 1733023060
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e98",
      "text": "[gpt.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023072
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd560aff09e0000047ebf",
      "text": "以下は詩の翻訳です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023072,
      "updated": 1733023072
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e9c",
      "text": "帰省は時間をかけるべきもの、落第の詩を閑かに吟ず。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e9d",
      "text": "高潔な心が道を惜しむ、世間の評判は才能を埋もれさせるようだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e9e",
      "text": "春雨が淮河に降り続き、暗い景色が広がる中、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047e9f",
      "text": "私船は馬を追うようにゆっくりと進む。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea0",
      "text": "別れの思いは惆悵を誘う、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea1",
      "text": "それも城に入る日を待ち望むゆえである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea3",
      "text": "詩の雰囲気を保ちつつ意訳しました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ea5",
      "text": "逐語訳して[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023065
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd55aaff09e0000047ebe",
      "text": "[gpt.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023066,
      "updated": 1733023069
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eac",
      "text": "以下は逐語訳です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023066
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eaf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb0",
      "text": "歸省值花時，閑吟落第詩。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb1",
      "text": "帰省は花の咲く時に値し、閑かに落第の詩を吟ず。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb3",
      "text": "高情憐道在，公論覺才遺。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb4",
      "text": "高潔な情は道の存するを憐れみ、公論は才能が遺されるを覚ゆ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb6",
      "text": "春雨連淮暗，私船過馬遲。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb7",
      "text": "春雨が淮河を連ねて暗くし、私船は馬を過ぎるに遅し。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eb9",
      "text": "離心可惆悵，爲有入城期。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047eba",
      "text": "離別の心は惆悵すべし、城に入る期があるがためなり。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ebb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd54aaff09e0000047ebc",
      "text": "原文の語順や表現を可能な限りそのまま訳しました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023050,
      "updated": 1733023050
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd547aff09e0000047e91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023048,
      "updated": 1733023048
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd59faff09e0000047ec0",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]「[落第]」とは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023135,
      "updated": 1733023286
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5a5aff09e0000047ec6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023142,
      "updated": 1733023142
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5a2aff09e0000047ec5",
      "text": "[gpt.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023138,
      "updated": 1733023142
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5a0aff09e0000047ec2",
      "text": "ここでの「落第」は、単に試験に失敗するという意味ではなく、特定の文脈では 科挙（古代中国の官吏登用試験）に落ちることを指します。科挙に落ちた学者が自身の状況を詩に詠むことは当時よくありました。この詩でも、自身の境遇を静かに吟じている情景を表しています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023136,
      "updated": 1733023138
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd59faff09e0000047ec1",
      "text": "\t試験に落ちて実家に帰るのか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023136,
      "updated": 1733023171
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5b7aff09e0000047ec7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023160,
      "updated": 1733023160
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5f5aff09e0000047ec8",
      "text": "[nishio.icon][惆悵]とは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023222,
      "updated": 1733023291
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5faaff09e0000047ece",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023226,
      "updated": 1733023226
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5f7aff09e0000047ecb",
      "text": "[gpt.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023223,
      "updated": 1733023232
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd600aff09e0000047ecf",
      "text": "「惆悵（ちゅうちょう）」は、物思いにふけり、心が晴れない状態や感情を指します。特に、別れや失望、孤独感からくる切なさや哀愁を表現する言葉です。この詩では、別れの悲しみや物寂しさが心に深く響いている様子を伝えています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023232,
      "updated": 1733023232
    },
    {
      "id": "674bd5f6aff09e0000047ec9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1733023222,
      "updated": 1733023222
    }
  ]
}